The Shatner Project - Season 1, Episode 4




Living & Dining Room

William and Elizabeth Shatner want to take advantage of their gorgeous valley views and bring the outdoors in. And they're going to do just that by knocking out the entire front of the house and opening up the living and dining rooms onto what is now an outdoor patio!




Original Air Date: 06-Nov-2014
